These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, spinach, asparagus, strawberry
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, dutch, indonesian
1. the italian is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person eating kiwi is the indonesian##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the left of the indonesian##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | strawberry | asparagus | spinach | kiwi   |
| Nationality   | italian  | nigerian     | dutch   | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, filmmaking, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, ice-hockey, lacrosse, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking | singing | card-games    |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | ice-hockey      | handball | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, gardening, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, epic, zombie
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | cooking | skydiving | gardening   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | epic | zombie | satire         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, scientific, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | martial-arts | family  | scientific      |
| Sport         | soccer | weightlifting   | lacrosse | snowboarding |

