.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, pear, banana, peach
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, guinea-pig, fish
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating banana##1
3. the person eating peach is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | peach | banana | pear | artichoke |
| Pet    | bird       | fish | guinea-pig | cat     |

