3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | colombian | italian | brazilian |
| Pet           | goat      | hedgehog | lizard | horse    |

