2. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | r&b | punk | d&b  |
| Pet           | cat | fish | dog       | guinea-pig |

