.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, dancer, software-developer, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, van, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the teacher##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | software-developer | pilot      | dancer | teacher |
| Transport   | bus          | boat | van     | snowmobile    |

