.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, australian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, ship, bike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the thai##1
3. the pakistani is on the left of the australian##1
4. the thai is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | australian | dutch | thai   |
| Transport     | ship  | bus    | airplane       | bike |

 